Ozar, left, serves as a consultant. LAWRENCE K. HO / Los Angeles Times; Photo, 
The Kindergarten Intervention Program is designed to prevent problems for 
youngsters like those, top left, at El Oro Way Elementary School. A group of 
mothers, top right, discusses the program at the school. 
</P>
