<P>
Golden West 115, Antelope Valley 61 -- Sophomore Shawna Armstrong scored a 
career-high 31 points to lead Golden West over Antelope Valley at Golden West. 
</P>
<P>
Armstrong scored 23 points in the second half, including 18 on layups. 
</P>
<P>
