<P>
AIR FORCE (U.S.); DEPARTMENT OF DEFENSE (U.S.) -- CONTRACTS; DEFENSE SPENDING; 
FINANCIAL DISCLOSURE; MISMANAGEMENT; ACCOUNTING; LYING; MILITARY AIRPLANES; B 1 
BOMBER (AIRPLANE); F 15 (AIRPLANE); F 16 (AIRPLANE); GENERAL ACCOUNTING OFFICE 
</P>
