NICARAGUA -- ELECTIONS; POLITICAL CAMPAIGNS; DEMONSTRATIONS -- NICARAGUA; 
ORTEGA, DANIEL; CHAMORRO, VIOLETA BARRIOS; POLITICAL CANDIDATES; FAVORITISM 
</P>
