RANDY LEFFINGWELL / Los Angeles Times; Photo, Bette Midler took best-record 
award for "Wind Beneath My Wings." ; Photo, Public Enemy's Flavor Flav, left, 
salutes rap winner Young M.C. JAYNE KAMIN-ONCEA / Los Angeles Times 
</P>
</GRAPHIC>
