MIDLER, BETTE; GUARDIAN ANGELS (ORGANIZATION); DEMONSTRATIONS -- LOS ANGELES; 
ANTI SEMITISM; PUBLIC ENEMY (MUSIC GROUP); GUNS N' ROSES (MUSIC GROUP); 
MCCARTNEY, PAUL 
</P>
