CAMPS; JUVENILE DELINQUENTS; JUVENILE INSTITUTIONS; INVESTIGATIONS; BODIES 
</P>
</SUBJECT>
</DOC>
<DOC>
<DOCNO> LA022290-0137 </DOCNO>
<DOCID> 179863 </DOCID>
<DATE>
<P>
February 22, 1990, Thursday, Home Edition 
</P>
