<P>
BOY PLAYING WITH MATCHES BURNS FACE 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<DATELINE>
<P>
EL TORO 
</P>
</DATELINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
An 8-year-old boy suffered second-degree burns to his face after he apparently 
set a cologne bottle on fire, authorities said. 
</P>
<P>
The boy, whose name was withheld because of his age, was playing with matches 
at his home in the 24600 block of Jutewood Place. The incident occurred around 
12:30 p.m. 
