film a commercial at UC Irvine. GARY AMBROSE / Los Angeles Times; Photo, COLOR, 
Bert Blyleven makes good on his T-shirt slogan in an informal workout of Angel 
players at UC Irvine. GARY AMBROSE / Los Angeles Times 
</P>
</GRAPHIC>
