<HEADLINE>
<P>
BETTING WITH BOB 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
Times handicapper Bob Mieszerski lost $30 when Akrokerami finished second in 
the third race Wednesday. Bob, who started the meeting with a mythical $1,000 
bankroll, is now at $707.80. 
</P>
<P>
Bob's bet today is a $9 triple from Haughty Notion, He's Illustrious and 
Broadway Pete in the sixth to Rolling Donut and Perforce in the seventh to 
Paper Princess in the eighth. 
</P>
<P>
Wednesday's Bankroll $737.80 
</P>
