<P>
Photo, Cancer benefit: Actress Tippi Hedren, chatting with Marty Golden, 
president of Concern Foundation for Cancer Research, was among celebrities 
donating their own art to Robert J. Leib Memorial Celebrity Art and Doodle 
Show. Feb. 8 auction at Triangle Galleries raised $60,000. BARRY E. LEVINE INC. 
