playing a lawyer who defends the underdog in "Class Action." STEVE BRAY; Photo, 
Corporate lawyer Mary Elizabeth Mastrantonio and people's advocate Gene 
Hackman, right, clash over car company lawsuit in "Class Action." ; Photo, 
