<P>
Dr. Ruth in Love: Dr. Ruth Westheimer will reportedly star in a half-hour ABC 
comedy series called "Dr. Ruth's House." The sex therapist will play Dr. Ruth 
Engelhof, who runs an off-campus rooming house near Albert University in 
Connecticut and who is romantically involved with the dean. Shooting begins in 
Los Angeles in April, but an ABC spokesman would not confirm when the show will 
air. BETH KLEID 
